{"type": "article", "id": 10507, "title": "Pot Cradle 绿植容器", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-08T07:06:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235721VEtRbOF0kaZhinK7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t首尔的 HEAN 设计事务所为小型绿植们设计了更灵活的安置方式。不再只是将花盆放在窗台、架子等平面上，你可以用这个名叫 Pot Cradle 的容器将你的小花朵、小仙人掌等绿色植物们悬挂在窗户、门锁、墙上的钩子等任何地方。Pot cradle 使用软性材料及可调节长度的抽绳，节省空间的同时，发挥创意将不同长度、颜色与悬挂背景搭配起来也成为一种独特的装饰。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235718NLMcuCpgaVwxqTQz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235719izQNBmauSnkclXoG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235719IHf58URYoG7OEAPc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235720yBpCXdrTvA04lqKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235720ABwbtncalSvkyNej.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235720tBeUSqIuoK0hGP3r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}